    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🗡️ How a Run Works</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Roguelike / Roguelite gameplay</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your difficulty and try to survive 20 rounds to complete a run.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy temporary upgrades in the shop between rounds - they reset each attempt.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn a chest after every round containing 1 or more equipment items.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can only equip one item per slot - for example, one weapon or one helmet.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Finish a run to permanently save your current loadout.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Die, and all new items are lost - you revert to your last saved loadout.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every 5 rounds, you can opt out and safely keep your new items.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027910/extras/a342a0b8a408cd2f356945698f8ead52.poster.avif?t=1764514805\" width=1170 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027910/extras/a342a0b8a408cd2f356945698f8ead52.webm?t=1764514805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027910/extras/a342a0b8a408cd2f356945698f8ead52.mp4?t=1764514805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⚔️ Enemies</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face five enemy types: Rats, Soldiers, Archers, Brutes, and Plague Keepers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover challenge upgrades in the shop that:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make enemies tougher</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grant them new abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reward you with extra coins instead of costing them</p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027910/extras/53a4c0e7e9410c0fa242370c27f24187.poster.avif?t=1764514805\" width=1170 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027910/extras/53a4c0e7e9410c0fa242370c27f24187.webm?t=1764514805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027910/extras/53a4c0e7e9410c0fa242370c27f24187.mp4?t=1764514805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >👑 Bosses</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight against five powerful bosses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each defeated boss increases loot quality.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your challenge:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spawn extra bosses for better rewards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or fight only the final boss at level 20</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat all bosses in one run for maximum loot and difficulty.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027910/extras/9e8c9ee66cf54965fbfedac289bb8afb.poster.avif?t=1764514805\" width=1170 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027910/extras/9e8c9ee66cf54965fbfedac289bb8afb.webm?t=1764514805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027910/extras/9e8c9ee66cf54965fbfedac289bb8afb.mp4?t=1764514805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔥 Difficulties</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock up to four difficulty levels:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Normal</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Heroic</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mythic</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Last Stand</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each difficulty:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Increases enemy strength</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adds new boss abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Improves loot quality</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Changes how each run plays out</p></li></ul>",
